project.name: Hero: Junkyard Engineering: The Wildest DIY E-Bike Builds

data.label: Style
data.name: w33s3 Dark
data.description: Dark, moody atmosphere with high contrast lighting. Cinematic composition with neon accent colors against deep blacks. Professional photography feel, dramatic shadows, rich color depth. Modern minimalist aesthetic, no text or watermarks.

data.label: Action
data.content: A gritty workshop scene at dusk, custom-built electric bike made from scrap metal and salvaged parts, exposed welds and riveted aluminum panels, warm overhead work lights casting dramatic shadows, grease-stained workbench with tools scattered around, industrial garage aesthetic with cyberpunk undertones, a triumphant DIY creation that looks both rough and beautiful
